flowchart TD

A[User types note into text field] --> B[User clicks Save button]

B --> C[Browser prevents default form submission]
C --> D[JavaScript event handler runs]

D --> E[Create note object: content, date]
E --> F[Add note to local notes array]

F --> G[Re-render notes list in DOM - no page reload]

E --> H[Send POST request to server /notes with JSON data]

H --> I[Server receives POST request]
I --> J[Server stores note]
J --> K[Server responds with JSON confirmation]

K --> L[Browser receives response]
L --> M[Console logs response; optional]